@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Consumer Flow

participant Consumer
participant KafkaClient
participant KafkaBroker
participant Topic
participant ConsumerGroup

Consumer -> KafkaClient: Create Consumer Instance
Consumer -> KafkaClient: Set Consumer Group
Consumer -> KafkaClient: Connect to Broker
KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Establish Connection
KafkaBroker --> KafkaClient: Connection Acknowledged

Consumer -> KafkaClient: Subscribe to Topic
KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Register Consumer Group
KafkaBroker -> ConsumerGroup: Add Consumer
ConsumerGroup --> KafkaBroker: Acknowledged

loop Poll for messages
    Consumer -> KafkaClient: Poll for Messages
    KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Fetch Messages
    KafkaBroker -> Topic: Read Messages
    Topic --> KafkaBroker: Return Messages
    KafkaBroker --> KafkaClient: Deliver Messages
    KafkaClient --> Consumer: Process Messages
    
    Consumer -> Consumer: Display Message
    Consumer -> KafkaClient: Commit Offset
    KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Update Offset
end

Consumer -> KafkaClient: Disconnect
KafkaClient -> KafkaBroker: Leave Consumer Group

@enduml

